{"tid":340743,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"女校辯論阿仙奴領隊去留 撐雲格留任勝","createTime":"2017-07-30T08:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T11:10:51.000Z","uid":4661,"like":116,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f5236f8009b01006bab2dce96c3e53fc1e2d145","tid":340743,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170730/s00006/b81a795ed80a10e489e2abbad94c18b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170730%2Fs00006%2Fb81a795ed80a10e489e2abbad94c18b6.jpg&h=b99c08d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲格退休對阿仙奴孰利孰弊，即使資深球圈人士和球迷都難有結論。但今早「鳴辯盃中學生辯論賽」就「雲格退休對阿仙奴利大於弊」的辯題，在香港華仁書院舉行了3場辯論，經一輪唇槍舌劍後，最終3場比賽均由反方勝出，「迷雲黨」完勝「反雲黨」。<br />\n<br />\n中學辯論普遍會以社會時事或民生熱話作辯題，但以外國足球，還要是阿仙奴的雲格作議題確是鮮有，故上星期題目一出，就引起網民熱烈討論，更吸引了近百人到場觀看。在3場對碰當中，其中一場由兩間女子中學- 正方的保祿六世書院，及反方的庇理羅士女子中學對壘，因睇波普遍被認為是男士的活動，故這場比賽更受關注。<br />\n<br />\n而在「試咪」時間，雙方同學均表明對足球認識甚少，但在過去1星期已全力準備，故都能出口成文。正方先拿出數據指，雲格近年在轉會市場吝嗇，又認為他常遲遲不與陣中主力傾續約，加上大牌球星阿歷斯山齊士等的周薪只有13萬鎊，與其他豪門差距甚大，造成常有隊長離隊的情況出現；正方續斥雲格戰術保守，並舉例他未能應對車路士的3後衛式，招致聯賽次回合完敗，又指雲格近年帶領兵工廠只奪得足總盃錦標，在歐聯已連續7年16強出局，故是時候退位讓賢。<br />\n<br />\n而反方則駁斥，雲格在阿仙奴多年著重青訓，令球隊可穩定發展，她們反駁雲格早年在轉會窗節儉，是由於球隊正在償還興建酋長球場的債務，若胡亂花費或會步列斯聯破產後塵；她們稱兵工廠在2013年還清債務後，已出錢購入奧斯爾和山齊士等球星，但強調阿仙奴「沒有曼城及車路士的油王，只有酋長，在睇餸食飯下已算有成績」，反方並以2012年曼聯在領隊費格遜退役後成績一落千丈做例，質疑雲格退休對阿仙奴利大於弊。<br />\n<br />\n最終3位評判亦因正方未能提出證明，引證雲格在退休後就能解決上述問題，並帶來更好成績等「利處」，故判反方庇理羅士女子中學勝出。而在同時間舉行的兩場辯論，同樣是由反方勝出，「迷雲黨」大獲全勝。"},{"pid":"d706d6feee9306977f4590e097c6f4311f61380f","tid":340743,"uid":3747,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:07:07.000Z","msg":"反雲是沒有出路的"},{"pid":"48c2e7909766313a85ac36f8781728c0512a73ba","tid":340743,"uid":127893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"有無可能搵到片 好想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fae670e526117c6ba74067fbcdca15508ee3d78","tid":340743,"uid":2218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248b0b8c14899d71ae5902b3c80ad5bdab7c3fb6","tid":340743,"uid":1585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"現叻又贏"},{"pid":"d2555681a5b64b7a08215c4e43130253e2ae5271","tid":340743,"uid":15853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464d79cf5e3a3e02a27516fb710706626fd18740","tid":340743,"uid":37303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:09:28.000Z","msg":"基本上抽籤撐雲已經宣佈嬴左啦"},{"pid":"fa583b239f847a2c76d8e3fa49c91d87dd50717f","tid":340743,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5e78571c94b97e0e60d61c9b4b79a5bdadf30b","tid":340743,"uid":5244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:09:55.000Z","msg":"代表全體妓多謝你地"},{"pid":"b3deef86228b2b6c1fc9d68bc64b7fea2a083574","tid":340743,"uid":2169,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:10:32.000Z","msg":"最終3位評判亦因正方未能提出證明，引證雲格在退休後就能解決上述問題，並帶來更好成績等「利處」，故判反方庇理羅士女子中學勝出。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 雲加未退休緊係證明唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069780fccb90abab67a5c6f9960ae089a217a3e4","tid":340743,"uid":43717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:10:48.000Z","msg":"雲加攞咗幾多錢出嚟，垃圾先需要啲咁嘅技倆嚟偽造輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd24bc7e2ca6946140e3ebe5b208c067fb9daf5","tid":340743,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:10:57.000Z","msg":"好想email比電叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fa4a067c001de1de51f6ef2635bcd7b8dd0036","tid":340743,"uid":60982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:13:50.000Z","msg":"迷雲黨never die"},{"pid":"6dd9dcde6c315d7d231d6893172803b8ef872475","tid":340743,"uid":24303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20603294e8fc9abf15fac413460edf550c4bb03","tid":340743,"uid":44457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:15:39.000Z","msg":"一星期準備黎講都算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5d7d21b6ca0bad9c79d3f46e495fee2d32404e","tid":340743,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:16:59.000Z","msg":"唔知幾位妹妹有無比爺爺吸引做阿迷"},{"pid":"6326277648473271ff720a0af2fefacf19a9b951","tid":340743,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"加埋尋晚大炒賓菲加 反雲黨好快d走啦"},{"pid":"4c8dcd4b32a3fc27a3ffb79ea0777180add0aa5a","tid":340743,"uid":6165,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hike.hk/load.jsp?route=ttam2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hike.hk%2Fload.jsp%3Froute%3Dttam2&h=97bb0dbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c3e64dea573065b106d81cf2582707baaef2ae4","tid":340743,"uid":6464,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:18:14.000Z","msg":"兩邊都打得差喎其實<br />\n反方係咁攞fa cup嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正方問有冇球員係以足總杯冠軍為目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反方又話阿仙奴成績好穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年第四都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咁講阿仙奴同曼聯架構好似 曼換咗費蛇就差 但佢地都證明唔到換走雲加成績就會下滑，又話換領隊洗多啲錢就好似leeds咁要降班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲係咁叫正方提出一個繼任人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇哂全場識波睇開波嘅聽會覺得好唔合理好好笑<br />\n其實正方理據係有，班妹唔識得捉住反方嘅盲點撚狗，例如管理球隊除咗財政之外，表現同成績都好重要，佢地冇講到成績差嘅話對阿仙奴有乜唔好處，總之係捉到鹿唔識脫角，而且班妹喺辯論技巧方面真係唔夠人地抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n場比賽好似係有兩個評判同分所以要計總分定勝負<br />\n所以迷雲都唔係贏好多咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d1589ed28e55420f12705b6da042f468147658","tid":340743,"uid":10670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:18:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一星期準備黎講都算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係男校搞 最尾可能辯到打交"},{"pid":"61f5b6d0dd863418226596c79edf863a77518c12","tid":340743,"uid":6165,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2015/05/wenger_always_optimistic.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmetrouk2.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F05%2Fwenger_always_optimistic.gif&h=25ce7a42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"894eb0ac04d7c54264d1990ea39c384b630aaeb0","tid":340743,"uid":12736,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20