"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反就係咁講冇爺爺冇球場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講近少少球場條數都找哂幾年啦</blockquote><br />\n球場條數好似未搞掂<br />\n但冇爺爺真係冇球場，格硬起都一定變中遊啦冇成績</blockquote><br />\n熱刺而家起緊<br />\n如果佢地都冇影響既話迷雲又少左個理據"},{"pid":"6e6bea7e6de6ae2e73f00e2db105993700aece72","tid":340743,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:29:42.000Z","msg":"撐雲加的都是英超其他19隊球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd152850b6b31a3dc993a421db99fe77182b1f8","tid":340743,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:30:01.000Z","msg":"你唔搵男校講屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15696bab1ee9505a7fefee18144346758f39defe","tid":340743,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係咁明  離任之後點係未知之數   留任試左咁多年證明係柒 將來既野全世界都無人預計到啦 ？ d評判on9？</blockquote><br />\n三個評判都唔睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n離任之後根本冇人講得清，就算成績差咁過渡期成績真係未必會好，好正常，樣樣野都要時間嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8926c789f86d4b4f9071edadfbd1e1fd8ab4e90f","tid":340743,"uid":10367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:30:57.000Z","msg":"帶隊穩定都唔提下8:2<br />\n穩定勁頭半季同賣隊長？"},{"pid":"c2cdb60e474a6848dccb6d23dbcfae4b7fc01d0a","tid":340743,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"根本睇評判咩迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87941c56394ed070c946b57071ff5d84482cc79f","tid":340743,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:31:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52161f6b2cf454a3a7b09e20b409b499a1d2f8b0","tid":340743,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兩邊都打得差喎其實<br />\n反方係咁攞fa cup嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正方問有冇球員係以足總杯冠軍為目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反方又話阿仙奴成績好穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年第四都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咁講阿仙奴同曼聯架構好似 曼換咗費蛇就差 但佢地都證明唔到換走雲加成績就會下滑，又話換領隊洗多啲錢就好似leeds咁要降班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲係咁叫正方提出一個繼任人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇哂全場識波睇開波嘅聽會覺得好唔合理好好笑<br />\n其實正方理據係有，班妹唔識得捉住反方嘅盲點撚狗，例如管理球隊除咗財政之外，表現同成績都好重要，佢地冇講到成績差嘅話對阿仙奴有乜唔好處，總之係捉到鹿唔識脫角，而且班妹喺辯論技巧方面真係唔夠人地抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n場比賽好似係有兩個評判同分所以要計總分定勝負<br />\n所以迷雲都唔係贏好多咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBtw果三個評判全部都唔識波的</blockquote><br />\n其實如果知道評判唔識波既話迷雲真係易贏，因為財政條數真係靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c366575d027b2a7f646a4330af95ffeb52d8e1","tid":340743,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係咁明  離任之後點係未知之數   留任試左咁多年證明係柒 將來既野全世界都無人預計到啦 ？ d評判on9？</blockquote><br />\n三個評判都唔睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n離任之後根本冇人講得清，就算成績差咁過渡期成績真係未必會好，好正常，樣樣野都要時間嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係<br />\n唔通搵曼做例子咩<br />\n隊隊波都唔同"},{"pid":"0493127eda388e457d0cb0fa1418ff959e843435","tid":340743,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:32:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶隊穩定都唔提下8:2<br />\n穩定勁頭半季同賣隊長？</blockquote><br />\n兩回合歐聯拜仁10比2都冇講<br />\n賣七個隊長就有講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8d66091460dfa5901bf236d12604a2cc630d70","tid":340743,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:33:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ba1df750614338c6b84215a4d1efe22843b738c","tid":340743,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:33:25.000Z","msg":"叫波台廢青落場仲好過啦"},{"pid":"0a2e1ddd62ee37d553f0789f907a406815f93e9d","tid":340743,"uid":71398,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:33:34.000Z","msg":"辛苦班學生妹，要蓋住良心扮反雲黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec712670faa7c2a63f93a78f37c507b31e2c9bb4","tid":340743,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6c831fedda40f757ad7a76f5ae1b9550bacc52c","tid":340743,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係咁明  離任之後點係未知之數   留任試左咁多年證明係柒 將來既野全世界都無人預計到啦 ？ d評判on9？</blockquote><br />\n三個評判都唔睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n離任之後根本冇人講得清，就算成績差咁過渡期成績真係未必會好，好正常，樣樣野都要時間嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能好過可能差過  留任就一定柒  因為未知將來點就話人證明唔到 ？ 將來既野點證明到？</blockquote><br />\n係，反方就係咁叫正方比個繼任人出嚟which is勁on9<br />\n比咗又點，我up個名出嚟就得啦，攤朵呀而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本冇人證明到未來雲加走係咪對球隊一定壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a89e183c972626f03170d7521927f8f92ccf6d5","tid":340743,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3afde7d491c47e1e0866b64c4fcf954d1e0f1230","tid":340743,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:34:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>帶隊穩定都唔提下8:2<br />\n穩定勁頭半季同賣隊長？</blockquote><br />\n兩回合歐聯拜仁10比2都冇講<br />\n賣七個隊長就有講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剩上季比熱刺炒2粒同騎著都已經抵炒"},{"pid":"cb5034c8689b801e90d3f03421a2817d33a2b856","tid":340743,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最終3位評判亦因正方未能提出證明，引證雲格在退休後就能解決上述問題，並帶來更好成績等「利處」，故判反方庇理羅士女子中學勝出。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 雲加未退休緊係證明唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁辯論黎做咩 戇撚鳩<br />\n正方真係多撚謝呢啲咁有水平既評判"},{"pid":"a070f165d51bc4475436f0dff847784d2b7f0422","tid":340743,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d74fffd389d1919e4451309b94d40c45af5d187","tid":340743,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:35:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"922997a5475f1a46ac61f9cb3a2cd08e4b451121","tid":340743,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:36:38.000Z","msg":"引用干地一上任就拎冠就引證倒換帥好處啦 正方咁撚廢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a97b826e2652ebdd4ab483484e7afcbb583565b","tid":340743,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1745ab74792c7ae3facd6c867c04e160bc8fb53","tid":340743,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:37:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係咁明  離任之後點係未知之數   留任試左咁多年證明係柒 將來既野全世界都無人預計到啦 ？ d評判on9？</blockquote><br />\n三個評判都唔睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n離任之後根本冇人講得清，就算成績差咁過渡期成績真係未必會好，好正常，樣樣野都要時間嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係<br />\n唔通搵曼做例子咩<br />\n隊隊波都唔同</blockquote><br />\n佢地就係搵曼聯做例子，話曼聯同阿仙奴結構好似，而曼聯正正就係換咗教練之後差<br />\n個問題係，阿仙奴未換教練已經差<br />\n同埋冇人可以保證邊一個教就一定會點<br />\n但呢個uncertainty係同去唔去求變冇抵觸嫁喎，你唔去改，就一定一成不變"},{"pid":"e43be01338e2eebb29129b3c075490f36ec9bf7e","tid":340743,"uid":21275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:37:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f1240a24a35d7e1698367ca874ef29f255134a8","tid":340743,"uid":1761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>引用干地一上任就拎冠就引證倒換帥好處啦 正方咁撚廢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個別例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n辯論呀依家"},{"pid":"d025f9535e8b45a7dbe38bcfb21a016a7a2b8e41","tid":340743,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:37:46.000Z","msg":"雲加又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b6bf8e6615918c597ee091bd89512a63578d77","tid":340743,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係咁明  離任之後點係未知之數   留任試左咁多年證明係柒 將來既野全世界都無人預計到啦 ？ d評判on9？</blockquote><br />\n三個評判都唔睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n離任之後根本冇人講得清，就算成績差咁過渡期成績真係未必會好，好正常，樣樣野都要時間嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能好過可能差過  留任就一定柒  因為未知將來點就話人證明唔到 ？ 將來既野點證明到？</blockquote><br />\n係，反方就係咁叫正方比個繼任人出嚟which is勁on9<br />\n比咗又點，我up個名出嚟就得啦，攤朵呀而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本冇人證明到未來雲加走係咪對球隊一定壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔走就有晒統計年年做拜仁私家雞</blockquote><br />\n今年冇得做啦"},{"pid":"e60f4430d7455af57b2d434164dfdd6bb180230f","tid":340743,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:38:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1ce652b9b5af21544b9168bb4b29141602387c4","tid":340743,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:38:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>引用干地一上任就拎冠就引證倒換帥好處啦 正方咁撚廢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個別例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n車有錢"},{"pid":"f01aab6beae5c5501680cfa52a0453669e6d470b","tid":340743,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>引用干地一上任就拎冠就引證倒換帥好處啦 正方咁撚廢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊同，雲加嘅話例子一定要係費蛇，沙夫，guy roux依啲先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb08907e55fae20d52ff87b071c3d42520ddec8","tid":340743,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:41:03.000Z","msg":"搵連登仔去<br />\n呢六仔友仔肯定輸到喊住走"},{"pid":"6917a85f14550cdaad3d186f96eb4e0d0bb7bf31","tid":340743,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:41:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最終3位評判亦因正方未能提出證明，引證雲格在退休後就能解決上述問題，並帶來更好成績等「利處」，故判反方庇理羅士女子中學勝出。</span>而在同時間舉行的兩場辯論，同樣是由反方勝出，「迷雲黨」大獲全勝。</blockquote><br />\n假設性問題點撚樣可以有證明呀，只可以推論嚟咋喎"},{"pid":"35972af4aa430b43910acaf58ab1d1d902b6bb1b","tid":340743,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:42:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最終3位評判亦因正方未能提出證明，引證雲格在退休後就能解決上述問題，並帶來更好成績等「利處」，故判反方庇理羅士女子中學勝出。</span>而在同時間舉行的兩場辯論，同樣是由反方勝出，「迷雲黨」大獲全勝。</blockquote><br />\n假設性問題點撚樣可以有證明呀，只可以推論嚟咋喎</blockquote><br />\n3位評判都on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbae7b173c211e1765c53d48b22144976f44d87","tid":340743,"uid":49304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:43:11.000Z","msg":"最終3位評判亦因正方未能提出證明，引證雲格在退休後就能解決上述問題，並帶來更好成績等「利處」，故判反方庇理羅士女子中學勝出。<br />\n<br />\n咁一早已經唔撚洗辯啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\non9咁唔通雲加留任可以解決到上述問題？雲加用左10鳩幾年證明俾你睇佢贏唔到冠兼上年第四光環都冇撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ce885cbfe83f548cc924245ed37697ffd7e34b","tid":340743,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"搵班唔識波既女仔黎傾足球，都仲可以講到頭頭是道，抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235f1e00c78a94718181aa1c5639508067cadf0e","tid":340743,"uid":18385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:44:55.000Z","msg":"雲加又贏<br />\n<br />\n支持雲加，沒有雲加，那有球場<br />\n阿迷應該飲水思源<br />\n佢地坐緊張櫈仔、睇既球場都係雲加起<br />\n咁大恩情，點可以叫雲加走<br />\n<br />\n仲未講經濟因素，每年財政收入良好<br />\n高層有花紅分，咁好既財政司點可以趕走人<br />\n<br />\n仲有歐洲賽因素，持續十幾年都可以去踢歐洲賽<br />\n即使今年亦都有歐霸入場券<br />\n歐霸唔肉酸，曼聯車路士都落力咁踢過拎盃<br />\n一樣光榮<br />\n<br />\n最後就係成績因素，雲加帶領下既阿仙奴拎過<br />\n無數獎盃，例如英超盃、足總盃、酋長盃，多不勝數<br />\n強如2016-2017既車路士英超冠軍，都輸左個足總盃比阿仙奴，使它奪下2016-2017既足總盃。如此輝煌成就，試問誰又能做到？<br />\n<br />\n總結，永續雲加！"},{"pid":"2f42a11a6fe6bb67d867a4b65d9a2248cc758808","tid":340743,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:46:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8209725bee85d2d9e1078c82bf63739cddec7f3c","tid":340743,"uid":18385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上無社局盾 重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌係，寫漏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f2fb8cc2c0022cdc882526fe6189b53fa210ec","tid":340743,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:48:07.000Z","msg":"反雲又豬"},{"pid":"a1b9544976268d1b53687bb0d6db48a9222930ae","tid":340743,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最終3位評判亦因正方未能提出證明，引證雲格在退休後就能解決上述問題，並帶來更好成績等「利處」，故判反方庇理羅士女子中學勝出。</span>而在同時間舉行的兩場辯論，同樣是由反方勝出，「迷雲黨」大獲全勝。</blockquote><br />\n假設性問題點撚樣可以有證明呀，只可以推論嚟咋喎</blockquote><br />\n3位評判都on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本一開波已經唔駛辯論啦如果咁，正方只可以假設，反方就可以用歷史打飛機<br />\n三個評判應該係迷雲黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17a0471e04b54ba6ca5931e691b359ce54807c9","tid":340743,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:49:40.000Z","msg":"條問題除咗有話題性之外其實垃圾到不堪"},{"pid":"f42a21ff838609a22efc6ca19c9b3c24487f5a47","tid":340743,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條問題除咗有話題性之外其實垃圾到不堪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d2b8e25c0c001d5716684f7a788be0b54a094a","tid":340743,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條問題除咗有話題性之外其實垃圾到不堪</blockquote><br />\n如果改做阿仙奴下季可以重奪英超應該精彩好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/